<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.generation-snes.fr/Forum/index.php?showtopic=183">http://www.generation-snes.fr/Forum/ind ... wtopic=183</a><!-- m -->
<br />Does this works with every 16mbit hirom game (with matching srma)? For example, does this tutorial with the great tool SWAPBIN works with Live-A-Live (the translated one of course)? I think it should work but i would like to be sure before destroying a cart:)
<br />
